{"tid":1140794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國解放軍少將嗆台獨：不認中國人又霸占寶島        要依法行事","createTime":"2019-05-06T05:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T06:34:25.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a22c1589b2c512ee76ce08cc852611baaa27a95b","tid":1140794,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"共軍少將嗆台獨：不認中國人又霸占寶島 要依法行事<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-06<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍少將羅援在環球時報發表署名文章稱，如果台灣方面不承認自己是中國人，又霸占著中國的寶島台灣，必須依法行事，這個法就是《反分裂國家法》。<br />\n<br />\n羅援在文章中稱，美國防部日前提交2019年度中國軍力報告，繼續誇大、抹黑中國的軍事活動。他指出，美方報告重點談到中國在南海的所謂軍事化行動，稱中國一直以來的軍事戰略都主要針對台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅援說，在國際上，南海被稱為南中國海，不是叫西美國海，美國憑什麼不遠萬里到南海來炫耀武力？美國連《國際海洋法公約》都沒簽署，有什麼資格在南海問題上指手畫腳？<br />\n<br />\n至於台灣問題，羅援宣稱，那更是中國的內政。他又說，中方多次承諾中國人不打中國人。如果台灣方面承認自己是中國人，兩岸無戰事。如果台灣方面不承認自己是中國人，又霸占著中國的寶島台灣，中方必須依法行事，這個法就是《反分裂國家法》。至於具體怎麼做，那是中國內政，美國無權過問。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3795603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3795603&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=1c7fb8ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3795603</a>"},{"pid":"8abbcc15b946cc3323556fe087992f698e414643","tid":1140794,"uid":64191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"中國人講法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fca75f28d6a82c74d4954b99afebda0b7800e98","tid":1140794,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:25:49.000Z","msg":"香港係香港人地方<br />\n支那人滾"},{"pid":"656b6a904ba81c3b00d910a31c2863dbc833958b","tid":1140794,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"地動山搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4555c25303dfd1548a7d8fe483bad3a85a9f7238","tid":1140794,"uid":22553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"支共送咗邊塊地比俄佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有蒙古國獨立呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a79eaef75a7a3b764a951b54a5f3af3e479528","tid":1140794,"uid":169529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"不認中國人又霸佔美國<br />\n不認中國人又霸佔地球<br />\n不認中國人又霸佔宇宙<br />\n我完全睇唔出佢句野有咩邏輯關係，如果真係咁可能成個銀河系都係中國<br />\n咁既智商配番咩國家既人真係無撚有錯"},{"pid":"3e97dda3b4a105114db2bf6c888c38a4a1994365","tid":1140794,"uid":18241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yh6xZE9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyh6xZE9.png&h=27aec13d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fa6b35e54ba5b548674ffa5f7a3f6e80cd4b374","tid":1140794,"uid":131600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"奔雷手：打啦 你地好悶丫"},{"pid":"bdca1adc2cb5767392b881d5df86857ec28a2f74","tid":1140794,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"你話事咩？"},{"pid":"7723ed8258241c1066e438e01282aec77ef09f52","tid":1140794,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a79eaef75a7a3b764a951b54a5f3af3e479528","tid":1140794,"uid":169529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"不認中國人又霸佔美國<br />\n不認中國人又霸佔地球<br />\n不認中國人又霸佔宇宙<br />\n我完全睇唔出佢句野有咩邏輯關係，如果真係咁可能成個銀河系都係中國<br />\n咁既智商配番咩國家既人真係無撚有錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"同中國人講邏輯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b4ce3d6f4d002fb1e83e8f4f877d446fd7382f","tid":1140794,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明已成歷史文件"},{"pid":"bae616b4d3f3154a9438f89b1081821bb74da6d9","tid":1140794,"uid":169529,"like":0